---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
const metadata = { title: 'About This Site' };
---
<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <div class="container mx-auto py-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">About This Site</h1>
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Mission</h2>
      <p>This website is dedicated to promoting the rich traditions of Taiwanese deities, temple culture, and folk customs. We provide bilingual (Chinese/English) content to help both local and international audiences understand Taiwan's vibrant religious culture.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Key Features</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
        <li>Multilingual support (Traditional Chinese & English)</li>
        <li>Comprehensive introductions to deities, temples, festivals, customs, and heritage</li>
        <li>Rich images and dynamic content</li>
        <li>User-friendly navigation and search</li>
        <li>Ideal for travelers, students, and culture enthusiasts</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Sources & References</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
        <li>Official websites of temples across Taiwan</li>
        <li>Open data from the Ministry of Culture, Religious Affairs Bureau, etc.</li>
        <li>Books and academic papers on folk beliefs and religious culture</li>
        <li>Original interviews and photography by our team</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Team & Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have suggestions, wish to collaborate, or need content authorization, please contact us via the "Contact" page.</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout> 